Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:29.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(200,200)}鯨の歌を聞いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:34.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(200,200)}運命を　感情を
